MID_支援_オロチ_カゲロウ_Ｃ: $t1$Wmオロチ|7$Wsオロチ|$Wa$E苦,|$w0|No... No... Where the hell is it?\nIt couldn't have vanished into thin air!$k\n$Wmカゲロウ|3$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E苦,|$w0|Orochi. What's with the worried look?$k$pWith the way you were wandering around,\ndid you happen to lose something?$k\n$Wsオロチ|$WaKagerou...$k$pOf all the people who could've found me,\nit would have to be you.$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E怒,|Is there a problem?$k\n$Wsオロチ|$Wa$E怒,|Well, to tell the truth...\nI lost one of my tarot cards.$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$WaYour tarot card...?$k\n$Wsオロチ|$WaYes. It was one of the cards\nyou drew just for me.$k$p$E苦,|I did my best to take care of them,\nbut now I can't find this card anywhere.$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E通常,|I see. In that case,\nwhy don't I draw a new card for you?$k\n$Wsオロチ|$Wa$E怒,汗|What?$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E笑,|You can reproduce the card\nif it's my drawing, yes?$k$p$E通常,|Or is there a proper fortune-telling\nprocedure that needs to be followed?$k\n$Wsオロチ|$Wa$E通常,|No, the cards themselves are easy to make.\nNo particular charms are necessary.$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$Eキメ,|Well then, not to worry.\nI'll draw a replacement right away.$k$p$E通常,|So this card you lost,\nwhat kind of picture was on it?$k\n$Wsオロチ|$Wa$E怒,|If I recall correctly, it was a\ndrawing of a brook and a fish.$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E笑,|I see. Then I'll draw the same thing.\nMind if I show you the rough sketch later?$k\n$Wsオロチ|$Wa$E苦,|Sorry for placing this on you, Kagerou.$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$Eキメ,|Don't apologize. We've been\nbest friends since we were young.$k$pIt's the least I can do\nto help a friend in need.$k\n$Wsオロチ|$Wa$E笑,|Kagerou...!$k$pI really am lucky to have a friend like you.$k$pThanks, Kagerou.$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E笑,|Sure thing. Leave it to me.\nI'll begin the preparations right away.$k$pNow, if you'll excuse me.$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wd$w0|$Wsオロチ|$Wa$E怒,|…………$k$p$E苦,|Ugh... I can't believe Kagerou\ndoesn't seem to remember that card...$k$p$E通常,|Well, she did say she'd go through the\ntrouble of drawing another one for me.$k$pI'll just keep my spirits up.$k
MID_支援_オロチ_カゲロウ_Ｂ: $t1$Wmオロチ|7$Wmカゲロウ|3$w0|$Wsカゲロウ|$WaOrochi. You mentioned you lost\nyour card the other day...$k$pI drew some roughs of a brook and a fish,\nalong with some other designs.$k\n$Wsオロチ|$Wa$E怒,|...Oh!\nYou've drawn a few other scenes, too.$k$pA mountain creek, a river and waterfall...\nWhoa, that one is particularly striking.$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$WaAre these drawings similar\nto the one you lost?$k\n$Wsオロチ|$Wa$E怒,汗|You know... on the other hand, something\nfresh might help shake off this mood...$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E怒,|Shake off...? Orochi.\nIs something the matter, by any chance?$k\n$Wsオロチ|$Wa$E苦,|...What makes you suddenly ask that?$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$Eキメ,|Give me some credit.\nThere's a reason for your long face today.$k$pI can tell when my friend\nisn't feeling her best.$k\n$Wsオロチ|$Wa$E怒,|Kagerou...!$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E通常,|Or is there something\nyou're unable to tell me?$k\n$Wsオロチ|$Wa$E苦,|No, that's not it at all.\nActually, only you would understand.$k$pThe truth is... the drawing on that card\nmeant more to me than the others.$k$pYou probably don't remember...$k$pBut the brook on the card was the same\nbrook where the two of us first met.$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E怒,|...!$k\n$Wsオロチ|$Wa$E怒,|You were training nearby with such\na determined look on your face...$k$pI lost track of what I was doing and\ndropped my basket of herbs into the river.$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E笑,|...And in the commotion,\nwe both ended up in the river.$k\n$Wsオロチ|$Wa$E通常,|Do you remember now?$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$Eキメ,|Of course. It was a childhood memory,\nbut it was shocking enough to stay with me.$k$p$E笑,|I still remember frantically gathering the\nherbs before they got lost downstream.$k\n$Wsオロチ|$Wa$E笑,|And after that...\nWe became pretty inseparable.$k$pI'm so glad you remembered, Kagerou.$k$p$E怒,|After our conversation the other day,\nit sounded like you'd forgotten...$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E苦,|I'm sorry, Orochi.$k$pI didn't make the connection between\nthe river and the drawing on the card.$k$pI must have come off as inconsiderate.\nI'm truly sorry.$k\n$Wsオロチ|$Wa$E苦,|You don't need to apologize!\nI'm the one who lost it in the first place!$k$pI felt so bad for losing that card,\nI wasn't sure how to tell you...$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E怒,|No. I should've noticed you were troubled.\nIt's clear that you truly treasured it.$k$p$E笑,|That alone makes me happy.$k\n$Wsオロチ|$Wa$E通常,|Is that so...?$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E通常,|It is, Orochi.\nCare to join me on a stroll?$k$pIncidentally, there's a river nearby that\nresembles the one near the capital.$k\n$Wsオロチ|$Wa$E怒,|What?! Really?!$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E笑,|I felt nostalgic when I stumbled upon it.\nI think it's a sign... Let's go together.$k\n$Wsオロチ|$Wa$E笑,|Really... In that case, count me in.\nLead the way, Kagerou!$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$Eキメ,|Sure thing.\nI'll take another stab at this drawing, too.$k
MID_支援_オロチ_カゲロウ_Ａ: $t1$Wmオロチ|7$Wmカゲロウ|3$w0|$Wsカゲロウ|$WaOrochi. About that drawing of the river...\nIt's finally complete.$k\n$Wsオロチ|$Wa$E怒,|Really?!\nKagerou, show me!$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$Eキメ,|Yes... Here it is.$k\n$Wsオロチ|$Wa$Eキメ,|Ohh! This ominous atmosphere...\nThe river's surface is churning about.$k$pScales of swimming fishes glittering\nin strange hues... I think I'm in love!$k$pThanks, Kagerou.\nThis will make a fine tarot card!$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E笑,|Is that so...\nYou're the only one to praise my drawings.$k$p$E苦,|Other people usually feel uneasy\nwhen I show my work to them.$k$p$Eキメ,|But if you're pleased with it,\nthen I'm happy as well.$k\n$Wsオロチ|$WaHehehehe... This drawing will\nboost my accuracy for sure...!$k$pI'll never let this card out of my sight.$k$p$E笑,|Likewise, I'm never letting\ngo of my best friend!$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E笑,|Hehe... So happy you're embracing me?$k\n$Wsオロチ|$WaNaturally! Words alone aren't enough\nto express this happiness!$k$pI'll have to throw my whole body into it～!$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$WaHeh, that so?\nI consider you my best friend too, Orochi.$k$pWhen I see that endlessly brilliant smile\nof yours, I can't help but feel warm.$k$pSuch an ability makes me a bit envious...\nBut I still can't help but adore it.$k$p$E通常,|I hope to always have\nyou smiling by my side.$k\n$Wsオロチ|$Wa$E怒,照|A-are you trying to embarrass\nme with all this sudden praise?!$k$pDon't ever say such things ever again!$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E笑,|Haha. I haven't seen you\nso embarrassed in a while.$k$pYour blush is simply adorable.$k\n$Wsオロチ|$Wa$E苦,照|Whaaat?!\nYou're just the worst today!$k$pKn-knock it off, Kagerou!$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$Eキメ,|Heh... When we act like this,\nit takes me back to our childhood.$k\n$Wsオロチ|$Wa$E笑,|Hehe. You're right.$k$p$E怒,|So many things have happened since then...\nBut my love for you has never wavered.$k$p$E通常,|From now on...\nWill you stay by my side?$k\n$Wsカゲロウ|$Wa$E笑,|Yes. I promise.$k
